			"value":"<p class=\"flavour\"><i>The shifting colors of this scarf reflect a common legacy, granting you power in the presence of your sibling-race allies.</i></p><p class=\"basics\"><b>Neck Slot</b><b>:</b> Uncommon</p>\n<p class=\"basics\"><b>Enhancement Bonus:</b> Fortitude, Reflex, and Will</p>\n<p class=\"basics\"><b>Properties:</b>\n<ul>\n<li>While you have a drow ally within 10 squares of you, you gain a +2 item bonus to Intimidate checks and Stealth checks.</li>\n<li>While you have an eladrin ally within 10 squares of you, you gain a +2 item bonus to Arcana checks and History checks.</li>\n<li>While you have an elf ally within 10 squares of you, you gain a +2 item bonus to Perception checks and Nature checks.</li>\n</ul></p>",
